==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Water snake
<hw>Wa"ter snake`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd>
<def>A common North American colubrine snake (<spn>Tropidonotus
sipedon</spn>) which lives chiefly in the water.</def> <sd>(b)</sd>
<def>Any species of snakes of the family <fam>Homalopsidae</fam>, all of
which are aquatic in their habits.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Water-soak</ent>⟦br⟧
